    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.35.1b" />
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>   
                Skyrim, Route 7<lb/>
                Columbia, Mo.<lb/>
                Jan. 3, '62
                    </dateline>
                    
                    <fw type="curatorial"><del/></fw>
                
                <salute>Dear Slade:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>I know I promised you a copy of the new printing of  <hi rend="underline">A Cycle</hi>. <hi rend="underline">Did</hi> I send you a copy? So much has been doing around here that I am not sure I sent you the copy.</p>
                
                <p>There is nothing new to tell, and you already know my feeling for you. It is unchanging</p>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">1</fw>
                    <pb facs="nei.j4c.35.1a"/>
                <fw type="authorial">-2-</fw>
                
                <p>I'm glad Xmas vacation is over. We begin again tomorrow, and the poor students have, by now, lost whatever momentum they had accumulated <hi rend="underline">before</hi> vacation. It's a bad plan, but what is the remedy? The trimester?</p>
                
                <p>Anyway here's the old affection for you &amp; Nita</p>
                <closer>
                <signed>John Neihardt</signed>
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
        <back></back>
